<body>
    <h1>Update AD Account Taxonomy Attributes</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 id=3D"UpdateADAccountTaxonomyAttributes-Overview"><strong>Overv=
iew</strong></h2>
<p>Ascension has a complex Active Directory infrastructure and account life=
cycle management where provisioning and de provisioning of identities are t=
aking place in multiple places. The lack of a single source of truth for th=
e identity management further complicates the user access reviews, terminat=
ion and rehire process.</p>
<p>In order to simplify the provisioning process with establishing appropri=
ate ownership of the relevant identities, ensure AD taxonomy attributes are=
 updated with appropriate values during creation of the Active Directory ac=
count (<strong>not sourced from HR</strong>). Also, true up taxonomy attrib=
utes for existing accounts based on their work relation identified in HR. R=
efer to the following tables for a combination of taxonomy attributes for n=
ew accounts.</p>
<h3 id=3D"UpdateADAccountTaxonomyAttributes-ProvisioningNonHRSourceAccount"=
>Provisioning Non HR Source Account</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"73=
002be2-a55a-4e1e-a957-1c087e911074" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Attribute Name</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Attribute Value</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Notes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>msexchExtensionAttribute34</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>CWR or EMP</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>msexchExtensionAttribute35</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Primary</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>employeeNumber</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>&lt;Generate Unique value&gt;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Generate a unique value and prefix it with SP_</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p>Attribute <strong>msexchExtensionAttribute34 </strong>will apply for all=
 AD accounts except AD-PRESENCEHEALTH.</p>
<h3 id=3D"UpdateADAccountTaxonomyAttributes-True-upExistingAccounts">True-u=
p Existing Accounts</h3>
<p></p>
<p>When a user is converted to and from CWR or EMP true-up existing users a=
ccount type (mxexchExtensionAttribute34) in the Active Directory based on t=
heir status in HR.&nbsp;</p>
<p>An existing user (employee) is converted as CWR, update accountType (mse=
xchExtensionAttribute34) for all linked identities as CWR.&nbsp;</p>
<p>An existing user (employee) is converted as EMP, update accountType (mse=
xchExtensionAttribute34)&nbsp; for all linked identities as EMP.&nbsp;</p>
<p></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
